details.name: Time Lapse
details.description: Weaver warps backward to whatever position it was in five seconds earlier--regaining the HP and mana from that time. No effect on cooldown, gold or experience. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter. DISPEL TYPE: Strong Dispel
details.upgrade_description: Reduces cooldown, and allows Weaver to cast Time Lapse on an ally.
